@EcoLens.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5133
@Token = your_jwt_token_here

### ============================================
### 认证相关 API
### ============================================

### 1. 注册用户
POST {{EcoLens.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

### 2. 用户登录（获取 Token）
POST {{EcoLens.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

### ============================================
### 出行记录 API 测试
### ============================================

### 3. 预览路线和碳排放（不保存到数据库）
POST {{EcoLens.Api_HostAddress}}/api/travel/preview
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "originAddress": "北京市朝阳区",
  "destinationAddress": "北京市海淀区",
  "transportMode": 3
}

### 4. 创建出行记录 - 地铁
POST {{EcoLens.Api_HostAddress}}/api/travel
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "originAddress": "北京市朝阳区",
  "destinationAddress": "北京市海淀区",
  "transportMode": 3,
  "notes": "上班通勤"
}

### 5. 创建出行记录 - 步行
POST {{EcoLens.Api_HostAddress}}/api/travel
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "originAddress": "北京市天安门广场",
  "destinationAddress": "北京市故宫博物院",
  "transportMode": 0,
  "notes": "步行游览"
}

### 6. 创建出行记录 - 公交车
POST {{EcoLens.Api_HostAddress}}/api/travel
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "originAddress": "北京市西单",
  "destinationAddress": "北京市王府井",
  "transportMode": 4,
  "notes": "购物出行"
}

### 7. 获取当前用户的出行记录列表
GET {{EcoLens.Api_HostAddress}}/api/travel/my-travels
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### 8. 获取单条出行记录详情（替换 {id} 为实际记录ID）
GET {{EcoLens.Api_HostAddress}}/api/travel/1
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### 9. 删除出行记录（替换 {id} 为实际记录ID）
DELETE {{EcoLens.Api_HostAddress}}/api/travel/1
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### ============================================
### 错误场景测试
### ============================================

### 10. 测试：无效地址（应该返回错误）
POST {{EcoLens.Api_HostAddress}}/api/travel/preview
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "originAddress": "不存在的地址123456",
  "destinationAddress": "另一个不存在的地址",
  "transportMode": 3
}

### 11. 测试：缺少必填字段（应该返回验证错误）
POST {{EcoLens.Api_HostAddress}}/api/travel
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "originAddress": "北京市朝阳区"
}

### 12. 测试：未授权访问（不提供 Token）
GET {{EcoLens.Api_HostAddress}}/api/travel/my-travels

### 13. 测试：获取不存在的记录（应该返回 404）
GET {{EcoLens.Api_HostAddress}}/api/travel/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

